calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">piranka</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Founded in 1991, <strong>Open Text</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OTEX\" title=\"Open Text Corporation\">OTEX</a></span>) is one of Canada's longest-running software companies. It has been highly successful over the years, growing to a market cap of $8 billion today.</p> <p>It has done this not by riding one</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1335295270/image_1335295270.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742226-open-text-not-quite-as-cheap-as-it-seems-but-still-a-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 08:15:19"}, {"id": "4742229", "title": "Box: Can Accelerate Growth To Mid-Teens", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1680324844/image_1680324844.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Getting over the hump - 4 balls\" data-id=\"1680324844\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1680324844/image_1680324844.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1680324844/image_1680324844.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1680324844/image_1680324844.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1680324844/image_1680324844.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1680324844/image_1680324844.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1680324844/image_16803248